  • Field Details

    • MINIMUM_FP_DIFF

      static final float MINIMUM_FP_DIFF
      Minimum absolute difference for floating point values. Values whose difference to the default value are smaller than this are considered equal to the default.
      See Also:
      Constant Field Values
